Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:11.23,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:15.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:22.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:26.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:30.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:33.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:36.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:40.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:44.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:48.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:50.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:54.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:59.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:02.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:11.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:15.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:18.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs185\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,175.389)}Gel Shocker's Debut!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,710.389)}The Last Day of Kamen Rider!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.60,0:01:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't be enough kindling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.02,0:01:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Micchi, let's go get some.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's go wash the rice.\N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.33,0:01:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That should do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's creeping me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounded like a person...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They're under the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me to Kamen Rider's\NTokyo headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't escape us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's replacement organization\Nhas no need for the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Micchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to take down the camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,These must be the girls I heard screaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta let HQ know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's too many for it to\Nbe an execution of traitors...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's Leader said something\Nstrange after I beat Rattlander.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He was going to erase Shocker\Nand create a new organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the new organization doesn't\Nwant the old Shocker combatants?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they're killing\Noff their potential liabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But... to even kill their\Nallies without mercy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The new organization their leader\Nmentioned is a force to be reckoned with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need to sniff them out ASAP,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,or they'll surely get the better of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Their first mistake was\Nleaving the bodies behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Searching the corpses could give us a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's construction here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty serious detour...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It went perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I followed the detour exactly,\Nbut it's just a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A dead end?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the new organization\Nthat took out Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it would be you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. It's time for Ganikomoru to shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the name of your new organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you,\Nbefore you depart this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire Shocker organization\Nhas been restructured!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And Geldam, the secret organization receiving\Nrigorous training in the African deserts,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,has been added to Shocker\Nas a shot in the arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us the name already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The name is Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Gel Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You think changing your\Nname will make you stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker is an unstoppable force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even need to dirty\Nmy hands with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker combatants, take care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So much stronger than Shocker combatants!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle with Gel Shocker\Nhas only just started.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here for the bodies\Nof the Shocker combatants!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me\Nand take the truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker... I will face you myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your struggles are pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ganikomoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use those Shocker bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to find your new Gel Shocker base!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You underestimate us, Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker does not make mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they do something to\Nthe truck while we were fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Gel Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I will track you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In just thirty seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the truck will blow up,\Ntaking Taki with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.77,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They put a time bomb on Taki's truck?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A... A time bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki, you're in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a time bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:21.16,Italics,,0,0,0,,A time bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd been one second later...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:11.13,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs55\c&H87CACF&\3c&H30312C&\bord4}Jonan University Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker's not that hot after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't even realize I smuggled\Nout one of those Shocker bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend at the university will\Nhave it analyzed by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That should give us a hint\Nas to Gel Shocker's whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now all remnants of Shocker\Nare banished from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, Ganikomoru's on the way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he get off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:50.45,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker's motorbike team, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're made up of top racers\Nfrom all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... face us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what you've got, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They just ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Losing their commander paralyzed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gradually coming to\Nunderstand Gel Shocker's hierarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Gel Shocker's base in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And who's their commander-in-chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I d-don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You think we'll buy that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The formation ceremony for Gel Shocker Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,will take place on Sarushima\Ntomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black will appear for the ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Their commander-in-chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The drug...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't take the drug\Nevery three hours... we die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'm done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Every three hours? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What a merciless way to\Nrun an organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So even if we capture their combatants,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we won't be able to hold them long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's interrupt their formation\Nceremony at Sarushima.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll see this "General\NBlack" while we're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange... there's no sign of anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:16:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You think they'll really hold the\NGel Shocker formation ceremony here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You think he put one over us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't see why he'd\Nlie knowing he was about to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to investigate to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let our guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:16:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try further in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming! Hongo, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ganikomoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So Sarushima really was a Gel Shocker base?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo. Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You've saved us the trouble\Nof going to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move, or Tachibana Tobei dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It will make a fine show for\Nthe Gel Shocker formation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what you want with us,\Nbut let Chairman Tachibana go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman Tachibana, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you need to have\Nyour eyes checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Look closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I came all the way from the African desert
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to manage the creation\Nof the Gel Shocker Japan Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember my name... General Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're General Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:31.14,Italics,,0,0,0,,This place will be your grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Steam?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.08,Italics,,0,0,0,,Don't bother struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:49.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,You're not strong enough\Nto break through that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good... they outwitted us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, if we get rid of this\Npipe, we can escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We will now begin the Gel Shocker\NJapan Branch formation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker, having acquired\Nthe resources of Geldam,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is now Gel Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker will surely conquer the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,To achieve this objective,\Nwe will kill, rampage, destroy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and perform innumerable acts of evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But as long as Kamen Rider walks the Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,even with Geldam on their side,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker will always suffer the same fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get out of that room?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.89,0:20:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We destroyed the pipe in the boiler room!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we used the heat to open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish you myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Capture General Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.97,0:21:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker will sow fear across Japan\Nat the command of General Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... you will not interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, General Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish that brat off!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Drill Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.10,0:22:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider's been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.81,0:23:05.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider seemed to die taking\Nout the Gel Shocker monster Ganikomoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:07.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will we see him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:10.68,Cont,,0,70,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:13.24,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(280.175,262.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.29,0:23:16.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I am General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.88,0:23:19.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider lies at the\Nbottom of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.40,0:23:22.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:24.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Go, Scorpiontokagesu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:30.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next week at this time,\Nwatch Gel Shocker in action!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:31.03,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,710.389)}Kamen Rider Dies Twice!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:50.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:57.96,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.96,0:24:01.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.71,0:24:05.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.53,0:24:09.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:13.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker's Debut!\NThe Last Day of Kamen Rider!!
Comment: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider Dies Twice!!